{"tid":650971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【剛果案】中國在商業範疇背信棄義　破壞香港普通法制度　外國投資者失去充分保障","createTime":"2018-05-02T18:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T08:44:51.000Z","uid":47714,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1a51e97c8dc3a9b3cdf9b9253db09a1800945c6c","tid":650971,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T18:57:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20110827/15561169\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20110827%2F15561169&d=51RUcZDpF0N1ha8sYjMM%2FXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=6d79de50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20110827%2F15561169&h=0c6ae761\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20110827/15561169</a><br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會昨日首度在本港終審法院主動要求釋法下，以全票通過有關外交豁免權的釋法草案。香港必須跟隨中國，對剛果民主共和國實行「絕對外交豁免權」，因此，該國欠美國一間公司8億元債務的案件，香港法院無權受理。有本港法律學者和立法會議員認為，日後商人跟有國家主權實體的背景公司做生意時，很可能會從此放棄在香港進行，「一定做少咗生意」。<br />\n<br />\n不能向外國追債<br />\n<br />\n中文大學法律學院副院長凌兵表示，今次本港法律跟從人大釋法後，以後商人不可能再在香港法院對外國國家或外國的政府追討欠債，「這對香港的營商環境會有一定影響」。<br />\n<br />\n或改到倫敦簽約<br />\n<br />\n涂謹申又認為，他日中國國企跟外國政府簽約時，亦很可能放棄香港，改為在可以追討外國國家或政府欠債的地方進行，例如倫敦，「因為到時倫敦先可頒令要求追債」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/8179/01百科-2011年由人大釋法的-剛果案\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F8179%2F01%E7%99%BE%E7%A7%91-2011%E5%B9%B4%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8B%E6%B3%95%E7%9A%84-%E5%89%9B%E6%9E%9C%E6%A1%88&d=51RUcZDpF0N1ha8sYjMM%2FXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e9a57a22\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/8179/01百科-2011年由人大釋法的-剛果案</a><br />\n<br />\n該次人大常委會釋法源於剛果民主共和國向在香港上市的「紅籌」中國中鐵（00390），批出開礦權，換取中國中鐵在剛果投資約131億港元於基建設施，但其後美國紐約一間基金公司FG Hemisphere Associates LLC以債權人身分，在香港興訟，要求中國中鐵把其中約8億港元投資額，為剛果民主共和國抵債。<br />\n<br />\n剛果民主共和國當時以「外交豁免權」，希望能阻止該美國基金公司向中國中鐵追債，但高院上訴庭依照普通法的「有限度豁免權」，裁定剛果民主共和國敗訴。剛果民主共和國不服判決，要求終審法院就外交豁免權提請人大釋法。<br />\n<br />\n2011年6月，終審法院5名法官以3比2票數，裁定此案需尋求人大常委會，就《基本法》第13條和第19條釋法。同年8月，第11屆全國人大常委會第22次會議通過決議，港府須跟從中央對剛果民主共和國實施「外交豁免權」。<br />\n<br />\n人大常委會法制工作委員會副主任李飛在解釋文件中指，中國奉行國家豁免原則，即中國法院不處理以外國為被告，或針對外國國家財產的案件，而國家豁免原則體現國家主權，屬外交行為，故據基本法第13及第19條，香港法院對外交無管轄權，故所有香港原有法例中，有關國家豁免的條文不得繼續適用。"},{"pid":"2c368a7544ae6179484d07003d51c235be99de53","tid":650971,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T18:57:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AlanLeongKahKit/posts/10157481614309691\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAlanLeongKahKit%2Fposts%2F10157481614309691&d=51RUcZDpF0N1ha8sYjMM%2FXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=26d99a7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AlanLeongKahKit/posts/10157481614309691</a><br />\n<br />\n梁家傑：在「一國兩制」中能保持香港一制的獨特性、價值和制度，對香港和國家都絶對有益、有利。現在我唯有講，雖然中共在民主和政治有關問題上背信棄義，要全面管治香港，但在其他事務，尤其在商業合約等範疇，外國投資者不用擔心得不到充分保障。"},{"pid":"15e722703d2068354647550b024c465df51e2d76","tid":650971,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T00:06:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d20687da9597c0558605c5be218f2dd87483a938","tid":650971,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T00:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8499dec646c86992f624cfc2e9e7daa231cb21","tid":650971,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T00:15:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38eaf7e78343a0f59602101c4a0c0b69f414e6e8","tid":650971,"uid":49588,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T00:40:23.000Z","msg":"中國大陸從來都不講法治！"},{"pid":"f55d3828fcb25aed2cc336b5ddf5b04cba0d3791","tid":650971,"uid":75448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T00:42:42.000Z","msg":"羸國又羸"},{"pid":"500c8b2f88384f75283f14209441e50eee6b03dd","tid":650971,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T01:28:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> 涂謹申又認為，他日中國國企跟外國政府簽約時，亦很可能放棄香港，改為在可以追討外國國家或政府欠債的地方進行，例如倫敦，「因為到時倫敦先可頒令要求追債」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n涂謹申又狗嗡<br />\n以貨船為例<br />\n香港船依家係去新加坡做仲裁多過去倫敦<br />\n因為新加坡有亞洲第一的國際商業仲裁法庭同中心<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.siac.org.sg/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.siac.org.sg%2F&d=51RUcZDpF0N1ha8sYjMM%2FXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=6def0044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.siac.org.sg/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.international-arbitration-attorney.com/zh-tw/arbitral-institutions-and-arbitration-courts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.international-arbitration-attorney.com%2Fzh-tw%2Farbitral-institutions-and-arbitration-courts%2F&d=51RUcZDpF0N1ha8sYjMM%2FXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=315e125b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.international-arbitration-attorney.com/zh-tw/arbitral-institutions-and-arbitration-courts/</a>"},{"pid":"ded7ac925a47e9950cb5e67c1447c0e18584ca79","tid":650971,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T07:12:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b471e5b385fbf1a8dbbbf280d6226e28c5cb3ea","tid":650971,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f55d3828fcb25aed2cc336b5ddf5b04cba0d3791","tid":650971,"uid":75448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T00:42:42.000Z","msg":"羸國又羸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T07:13:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/151327_819112c12de3e5baba111d98b537490b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F151327_819112c12de3e5baba111d98b537490b.png&h=e37aef9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/151332_8169b091ed9a14f173810906701f5ab8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F151332_8169b091ed9a14f173810906701f5ab8.jpg&h=c01414cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1db03cf67fe1c866a52a46870632691f5d7dfcb","tid":650971,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:06:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c696777c81e8bbed255c15f67bf4a5154d38c37","tid":650971,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c1a239633ee23cde12b9b1f40884b1d7ca6f56d","tid":650971,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:44:51.000Z","msg":"司法真係仼支共講<br />\n<br />\n美國幾時取消關係法"}]}